---
import Layout from 'layouts/Layout.astro';

import Footer from 'components/common/Footer.astro';
import Header from 'components/common/Header.astro';
import ExperinceCards from 'components/ExperinceCards.astro';
import Marquee from 'components/Marquee.astro';

export interface Props {
  title: string;
}

const { title } = Astro.props;
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <Header />
  <div class="p-4 font-sans text-slate-200">
    <h1 class="text-3xl">ðŸ‘‹ Hi I am Amit Chongbang</h1>
    <section class="my-4 flex flex-col text-lg">
      <h2 class="text-2xl">About</h2>
      <p class="my-4">
        I am a software developer based in Perth, Australia. I am passionate about building
        high-quality web applications and mobile apps. My skills spans to a wide range of creative
        and technical displinces, which are from web development, backend development and mobile
        application development.
      </p>
      <p class="my-4">
        My aim is to provide solutions for any problem with my experience and skillsets. Plus as
        well as to expand my knowledge by creating and developing new web applications with
        different tech stacks.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="my-2">
      <h2 class="my-4 text-2xl">Experinces</h2>
      <ExperinceCards />
    </section>

    <Marquee />

    <section class="my-4">
      <h2 class="my-4 text-2xl">Interests</h2>
      <p>
        As a software engineer, my passions extend beyond the digital realm into the tangible world of electronics, mechanical work, camping, and hiking. 
        In programming, I find the creative challenge of problem-solving exhilarating, constantly seeking elegant solutions to complex problems. 
        Exploring the intricacies of electronics allows me to understand the inner workings of technology, from circuit design to microcontroller programming, bridging the gap between software and hardware. 
      </p>
      <br/>
      <p>
        Engaging in mechanical work fuels my curiosity for how things function, from tinkering with engines to crafting intricate mechanisms. 
        When I'm not immersed in code or engineering projects, you'll often find me amidst nature, seeking solace in the tranquility of the wilderness through camping trips and invigorating hikes, where every trail offers a new adventure and perspective.
      </p>
    </section>

  </div>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
